On motion to dismiss appeal. Appeal dismissed December 16, 1924. J. A. HARRIS v. J. S. LEBB, SECURITY SAVINGS & TRUST CO. et al. (231 Pac. 187.)

(No Syllabus.)

Messrs. Chamberlain, Thomas é Kraemer, for the motion. *43No appearance contra. McBRIDE, C. J.

The facts in this case are the same as the facts in the other case of Harris v. Lebb, decided this day, and for the reason there 'given the appeal is dismissed.

Appeal Dismissed.
